# Development
Mediator: Always use Mediator.NET CQRS pattern for API endpoints
Error: Use ErrorOr for returning appropriate errors

# Integration tests

Favour integration tests over unit tests where ever possible, but unit test if fine if worth it.

Always use Microsoft WebApplicationFactory for integration tests

WireMock: Use WireMock .NET for mocking APIs when needed

NSubstitute: Use NSubstitute for mocking object wherever needed

AutoBogus: Use Bogus/Auto Bogus for generating test data

FluentAssertions: Use FluentAssertions for assertions

TestContainers: Use TestContainers for setting up database during integration tests
